law.catch_line: Use of agencies' existing diabetes information, data, initiatives, and programs to implement KRS 211.751 and 211.752.
law.text: The requirements of KRS 211.751 and 211.752 shall be limited to the diabetes information, data, initiatives, and programs within each agency prior to June 8, 2011, unless there is unobligated funding for diabetes in each agency that may be used for new research, data collection, reporting, or other requirements of KRS 211.751 and 211.752.
law.history: Created 2011 Ky. Acts ch.83, sec.3, effective June 8, 2011.
